  <brief_title>Beta-CIT-SPECT and Neurophysiology in Depression</brief_title>
  <official_title>Serotonin and Dopamine Transporter (SERT, DAT) Availabilities as Assessed by b-CIT and SPECT, and Neurophysiological Measures of Central Serotonergic Activity in Patients With Depression Under Treatment With Escitalopram</official_title>
  <sponsors>
