  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Aim of this project is to investigate the effects of escitalopram on monoamine transporter
      (SERT, DAT) availabilities as assessed by b-CIT and SPECT, and on neurophysiological
      parameters such as the loudness dependence of auditory evoked potentials (LDAEP) in patients
      with depression.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
